snippet.textDisplay:
The creative energy is soaring in this song. The concept, lyrics, cinematography, set, costume, music, direction, singers and choreography is so on point. Kudos to all the artists in front of the lens who are engaged in creating this mesmerising energy that transfers itself through the video. 

The line 'sanu loki kehnde super cool... wakhre asool' 2:09 paired with the amazing dancers and their energy resonates so deeply. We are a terribly misunderstood nation and this is not only a blockbuster song but a testament to the fact that this generation is not afraid of embracing their identity/ culture and is celebrating it! 

Thank you to the entire team for creating this masterpiece!
